21 sellers and nonremote sellers.
22 Prior to December 1, 2026, the department shall provide the reports required by
23 this section for the years 2019, 2020, 2021, 2022, 2023, 2024, and 2025.
24 Section 3. That a NEW SECTION be added to chapter 10-12A:
25 If the department does not have the information necessary to furnish a report to
26 an Indian tribe a tribal government pursuant to sections 1 and 2 of this Act, the
27 department must develop and maintain a methodology to collect and report the
28 information.
